FeedPackage.Description:
A library containing classes for working with powershell: This is a Monolithic build (everything merged in, no dependencies)
- Trivial dynamic powershell invocation from C# - RESTable cmdlets (so you can host cmdlets via a REST service and call them either remotely or locally)
[Note: This library is not quite ready for public consumption--I'm in the middle of some code reorganization]
FeedPackage.ReleaseNotes: Initial Build of the new ClrPlus Powershell package.
FeedPackage.Summary: A library containing classes for working with powershell.
FeedPackage.Title: ClrPlus.Powershell
